        <strong>2. Use the visual dropdowns.</strong> Select values for Minute, Hour, Day, Month, and Weekday from the dropdowns. Each dropdown includes common shorthand options like "Every minute," "Every 6 hrs," and "Weekdays" alongside specific numeric values. The expression field updates in real time and the <strong>Plain English</strong> panel explains what the schedule means in plain language.
